App Name: Tic Tac Toe
Developer: Smirking Owl Studio
Co-Developer: Deep Vision Solution

Effective Date: 26-05-2025

This Privacy Policy describes how Tic Tac Toe, developed by Smirking Owl Studio, handles user information. We are committed to protecting your privacy.

1. Information We Do Not Collect
We do not collect or store any personal information from users. This means:

No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or other identifiers

No usage or gameplay analytics

No location data

2. No Third-Party Services
The game does not use third-party services or SDKs such as:

Analytics services

Social media integrations

3. Children’s Privacy
Tic Tac Toe is suitable for all ages. Since we do not collect personal data, we fully comply with privacy regulations for children, including COPPA (Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act).

4. Data Storage
As no data is collected or stored, there is no risk of data misuse or loss. All gameplay takes place locally on the user's device.

5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. If we make any changes, we will update the "Effective Date" above. Continued use of the app after changes implies acceptance of the new policy.

